{"data": [{"id": "4741515", "title": "ONEOK: Benefitting From Recent Acquisitions", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA, Texas, Midland, Permian Basin Petroleum Museum, dusk\" data-id=\"200436389-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">USA, Texas, Midland, Permian Basin Petroleum, dusk</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Walter Bibikow/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I\u2019m not enthusiastic about seeing my EnLink units (which have been earning a strong free cash flow) diluted into a larger company. I view the acquisition of EnLink (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ENLC\" title=\"EnLink Midstream, LLC\">ENLC</a>) by ONEOK (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKE\" title=\"ONEOK, Inc.\">OKE</a></span>) as net negative for EnLink</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741515-oneok-benefitting-from-recent-acquisitions-oke-enlc-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:15:49"}, {"id": "4741512", "title": "Rocket Pharmaceuticals: Not Bad Valuation But Reflexivity Risks Remain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman, computer screen and dna \u200bfor lab research or gene therapy or anti aging science, futuristic or innovation. Female person, pointing and double helix for medical tech, chromosome or chemistry\" data-id=\"2148853421\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1069px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(