.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Justin Paget</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>) is a company that, we believe, is heavily overvalued, as discussed in our large article, where we shared how the company's share price run-up <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4735229-tesla-election-victory-doesnt-change-core-concerns\">doesn't change the core concerns</a>. As we'll see</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741508-tesla-upcoming-government-double-whammy", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:52:15"}, {"id": "4741506", "title": "SPYD: High-Yield Might Have More Risk Than Benefit", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"growth in business and finance, growing graphs and charts\" data-id=\"1795167728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">anyaberkut</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h3><strong>Thesis</strong></h3> <p>High-yield stocks investing has been a rather niche strategy over the past years, as the majority of investors target more growth, or at least dividend-growth-oriented investments. As a result of strong gains in the growth universe over the past decade, high-yield stocks have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741506-spyd-high-yield-might-have-more-risk-than-benefit", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:49:11"}, {"id": "4741505", "title": "T-Mobile: Answering The Call For Further Growth, Shareholder Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.co