ngalpha.com/article/4741505-t-mobile-stock-further-growth-shareholder-returns-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:45:09"}, {"id": "4741504", "title": "Columbia Sportswear: Undervalued, Positioned For Growth", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Men\"s Jogging supplies shot knolling style.' data-id=\"641229891\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5786px\" height=\"4353px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yagi Studio</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>In my view, Columbia Sportswear (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COLM\" title=\"Columbia Sportswear Company\">COLM</a></span>) has a lot of tailwinds ahead with reasonably priced clothing and great fabric technologies. The company also has performed subpar in recent years, with below-average financial growth across many metrics. Though has a strong</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741504-columbia-sportswear-undervalued-positioned-for-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:38:17"}, {"id": "4741502", "title": "Qualcomm: Auto Business Offers Material Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Qualcomm Snapdragon MSM7227A\" data-id=\"1196326348\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-capti